briefTitle: Mobile Phone Multimedia Messaging Intervention for Breast Cancer Screening
officialTitle: Mobile Phone Multimedia Messaging Intervention for Breast Cancer Screening: Intervention Phase
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Korean American immigrant women
* Aged 40-79
* Residence in Minnesota
* Possession of mobile phone with text-message function
* Possession of active email account

Exclusion Criteria:

* Mammogram receipt within the past 2 years
